          To contact us immediately, our email is <a class="bold-text-link" href="mailto:info@reyalperformance.com"
            target="_blank" rel="noopener">info@reyalperformance.com</a> and instagram <a class="bold-text-link"
            href="https://www.instagram.com/reyalperformance/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">@reyalperformance</a>.
